snippet.title: Buns: Bunny Survivor - A Vampire Survivors-inspired action roguelike game made with PICO-8!
snippet.description:
Play for free on itch.io https://unikotoast.itch.io/buns-bunny-survivor?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Kill enemies, collect gems, choose upgrades and kill the final boss. Small roguelike game heavily inspired by vampire survivors and shmup games.
